WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.262
=Episode 23=

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:08.800
(Dad likes cilantro.)

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:10.680
(A lot of cilantro.)

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:12.280
(I can't stand the smell.)

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:13.440
(But I'll put up with it.)

00:01:14.160 --> 00:01:14.880
(Oh, right.)

00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:16.840
(Dad likes watching financial news.)

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:17.840
(Every Monday, Wednesday, and Friday.)

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:19.960
(He never misses BBC News
in the morning.)

00:01:19.960 --> 00:01:21.760
(Remember to download it for him
in advance.)

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:24.440
(Try to let Dad drink less red wine.)

00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:25.400
(His stomach isn't good.)

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:27.040
(Red wine gives him acid reflux.)

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:31.000
(Dad and Mom's anniversary
is September 10th. Teacher's Day.)

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.680
(Mom's death anniversary is the
sixth day of the fourth lunar month.)

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:36.000
(Remember all these dates.)

00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:41.800
Is Zhu gone

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:45.040
because of me?

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:47.040
Are you blaming me

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:48.960
for breaking up your family?

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:51.840
You think Shen Qi's death
was because of me?

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:01.160
Shen Qi was my best friend in college.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:05.480
All these years I've been with you,

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:07.440
I've always felt guilty.

00:02:07.440 --> 00:02:08.480
Do you know?

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:14.440
Because I believed you loved me.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:17.480
You said I was beautiful.

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.360
But you're just a dog that never learns.

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:23.520
Don't think I don't know

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:25.400
who that woman beside you is now.

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:27.760
I was really blind.

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:28.640
I...

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:29.960
I was really blind.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.880
Lu Jiaming, you're a jerk!

00:02:34.180 --> 00:02:35.360
You're right about everything.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.440
She's divorced now.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.680
Don't you need a secretary?

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:55.960
Hire her.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:56.960
She's very capable.

00:02:57.080 --> 00:02:58.600
I don't need one. You...

00:02:58.600 --> 00:03:00.760
You do.

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:02.200
Fine, I do.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:04.480
I'll listen to you.

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.480
You're the best, Dear.

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:09.120
Done.

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:10.880
Work hard here.

00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:13.360
I'll get going then.

00:03:13.370 --> 00:03:14.280
You're leaving already?

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:15.800
I have plans.

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:16.800
Bye-bye.

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:18.000
Bye-bye.

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:27.960
Qingbai?

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:28.880
Mm.

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:30.200
Oh.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.560
Right.

00:03:33.600 --> 00:03:35.300
Do you know
how to use the coffee machine?

00:03:35.600 --> 00:03:36.400
I know.

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:39.200
Could you make me a latte?

00:03:40.320 --> 00:03:41.920
Sure. I'll go make it now.

00:03:59.080 --> 00:03:59.880
Thank you.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.800
Your eyes look like someone's.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.360
Like who?

00:04:16.960 --> 00:04:17.760
Like...

00:04:21.400 --> 00:04:22.680
Forget it.

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:23.920
Alright.

00:04:23.960 --> 00:04:27.480
Go to HR and complete the onboarding.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:29.080
Okay.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:33.840
Today,

00:04:34.760 --> 00:04:36.560
we did something incredible.

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:38.640
Yeah.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:42.720
Sun, you gave me the courage.

00:04:44.920 --> 00:04:45.760
But

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:49.160
what about your mom?

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:56.520
Didn't you tell me before?

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:57.920
Love

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:00.960
means being fearless
in the face of obstacles.

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:06.120
Since they've decided to divorce,

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.960
I'm no longer your brother.

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:16.280
I knew it.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.920
We wouldn't lose.

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:23.200
Don't worry.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.200
I won't let you lose either.

00:05:36.280 --> 00:05:37.840
What about Ms. Fan?

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.680
Ms. Fan who got engaged

00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:43.520
and then broke it off without regret?

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:46.120
She's flying to the US tomorrow.

00:05:47.300 --> 00:05:48.980
I'm going to the airport
to send her off.

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:50.600
And

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:52.880
thank her.

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:55.760
Thank her?

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:12.280
Made up your mind?

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:13.360
Are you staying?

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:19.240
Not leaving.

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:24.240
What about you two?

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:37.040
Love means being fearless
in the face of obstacles, right?

00:06:39.160 --> 00:06:40.080
Alright.

00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:44.240
Then I wish you happiness.

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:48.080
Thank you.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.880
Do you remember

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:15.160
the prank you played on me
the first time I came to the Lu family?

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:18.560
I do.

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:19.640
Back then, I thought

00:07:19.640 --> 00:07:20.880
you were really troublesome.

00:07:23.280 --> 00:07:24.360
A hard nut to crack.

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:29.640
Later, you tried to scare me away.

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:31.800
You were afraid
I'd take your family fortune, right?

00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:34.720
At that time, I was thinking,

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:35.880
how could there be

00:07:35.880 --> 00:07:37.960
such a money-obsessed rich girl?

00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:43.920
So you investigated me.

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:01.880
Didn't you investigate me too?

00:08:11.937 --> 00:08:12.760
Does this count as

00:08:12.760 --> 00:08:15.660
the great reconciliation of the century
after all that testing each other?

00:08:17.640 --> 00:08:19.000
Accept the surgery.

00:08:21.300 --> 00:08:23.040
Only then can there
be true reconciliation.

00:08:25.287 --> 00:08:26.167
I'm scared.

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:28.280
Scared of what?

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:31.560
What if one day I'm gone?

00:08:43.600 --> 00:08:45.160
You must go through with the surgery.

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:47.760
Don't think nonsense.

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:49.160
Alright?

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:09.360
I'm moving out today.

00:09:22.575 --> 00:09:24.387
I asked your dad for a breakup fee.

00:09:25.150 --> 00:09:26.310
It's not much to ask, is it?

00:09:27.912 --> 00:09:29.600
You don't have to tell me these things.

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:33.000
Now that things are like this,

00:09:33.762 --> 00:09:35.962
there's no need
to hide some things from you.

00:09:36.512 --> 00:09:38.472
I was the one who called Lily Fan back.

00:09:39.150 --> 00:09:40.630
Ye Man's feelings for you

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.280
have never changed.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:45.160
And the pregnancy,

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:48.160
I faked that too.

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:50.520
I framed you.

00:09:52.160 --> 00:09:53.280
I'm sorry.

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.760
As for what happened with your mom,

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:02.600
I don't know how to explain it.

00:10:04.160 --> 00:10:06.600
I've always believed
that loving someone isn't wrong.

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:09.320
Just like how you love Man,

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:11.160
you'd risk everything.

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.560
It's just that your mom and I
were both unlucky.

00:10:19.975 --> 00:10:21.500
We loved the wrong man.

00:10:27.900 --> 00:10:28.575
Sun,

00:10:29.280 --> 00:10:31.160
you must've suffered a lot growing up

00:10:32.100 --> 00:10:33.920
without your mom by your side.

00:10:36.175 --> 00:10:37.560
Now, I'm giving the Lu family,

00:10:38.575 --> 00:10:39.615
your dad,

00:10:41.080 --> 00:10:41.880
and Man,

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:45.440
all to you.

00:10:48.760 --> 00:10:50.200
Take it as my compensation.

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:52.480
Ms. Huang.

00:10:55.080 --> 00:10:56.120
Wait a moment.

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:58.280
I'm going to get something for you.

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:11.600
Putting everything else aside,

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:14.120
you were probably
my mom's best friend.

00:11:16.312 --> 00:11:17.032
This is for you.

00:12:34.975 --> 00:12:39.475
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:12:39.700 --> 00:12:43.488
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:12:43.663 --> 00:12:47.738
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:12:47.738 --> 00:12:51.875
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:55.775
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:12:55.775 --> 00:12:59.550
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

00:12:59.550 --> 00:13:01.825
♪The you in my memories♪

00:13:01.825 --> 00:13:03.838
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:13:03.838 --> 00:13:09.275
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:13:10.838 --> 00:13:16.275
♪Forget you completely?♪